## Project

App: **Ngày Lành Tháng Tốt** (ngaytot / ngaylanhthangtot.vn)
Stack: React Router v7 (Vite) · Supabase (DB + Auth + RLS + Edge Functions) · Vercel · Tailwind CSS · Direction C design system (`app/components/brand/` — `CBottomNav`, `CSegmented`, `CTopStrip`)

## Architecture summary

- **Frontend:** React SPA on Vercel. Pre-render **`/`** for SEO; PWA **`start_url`** → **`/splash`**. Authenticated routes under **`/lich`**, **`/tra-cuu`**, **`/toi`** (layout: `authenticated.tsx`). Legacy **`/app/*`** 302 via `nav-config` during transition.
- **Backend:** Supabase only. Client via publishable key + JWT; **RLS** is the auth boundary.
- **Server logic:** Edge Functions — **Bát Tự** proxy (`BAT_TU_*` secrets), **PayOS** checkout + webhook, share resolve/OG, `generate-reading-day` / `generate-reading-la-so` / `generate-reading-tieu-van` (Gemini), cron push. No PayOS, Bát Tự or Gemini calls from the browser.
- **Design:** Direction C — lịch-tờ metaphor; forest-deep `#0e1c14` for ceremonial surfaces; 3-tab nav (Lịch · Tra cứu · Tôi). Source: `artifacts/design/ngaylanhthangtot-vn/` + `app/components/brand/`.

## What this app does

Vietnamese B2C PWA: **subscription calendar** (“Lịch ngày lành cho riêng bạn”) using **Bát Tự Tứ Trụ** personalized by saved lá số. **PayOS** subscription + add-on luận (no lượng in UI). Anonymous: landing-only teaser (no public `/lich`). Tone: calm, specific, Vietnamese.

## Not building (out of scope)

Generative chatbot; raw almanac tables as primary UI; marketplace thầy; community/UGC; AI-personalized push; non-Vi locale; admin dashboard; credit gifting; offline engine; auto-recurring subscriptions; **self-serve birth-data edit** (birth-data is set once at onboarding — no edit form anywhere in the app); **multi-person stored "family profiles"** (dropped in Direction B — not built at all).

## LLM / AI Reading (first-class feature)

AI Reading (Luận Giải) is first-class, powered by **Gemini Flash** via `generate-reading-day`, `generate-reading-la-so`, and `generate-reading-tieu-van`. Engine = deterministic Bát Tự + Gemini templates. No generative chatbot. No raw LLM access from the browser. Gating: **subscription + entitlement columns** (`bazi_reading_unlocked_at`, `tieu_van_reading_expires_at`).

## AI module boundary

Gemini calls live exclusively in `supabase/functions/generate-reading-{day,la-so,tieu-van}/` (shared handler in `_shared/generate-reading/`). No AI SDK in the React app. RLS + `subscription_expires_at` / entitlement helpers (`app/lib/entitlements.ts`, `_shared/entitlements.ts`) enforce auth/payment boundary.

## Key constraints

- **Auth:** Google OAuth + email/password; **anonymous** browse for free calendar/teaser.
- **PayOS only** — no Stripe unless product changes.
- **Feature credit keys:** DB canonical names in `feature_credit_costs`.
- **PayOS `package_sku` (checkout):** `goi_1thang`, `goi_6thang`, `goi_12thang`, `luan_bat_tu`, `luan_tieu_van`. Legacy `le` webhook-only. UI route: **`/dat-lich`**.
- **Screen inventory:** `app/routes/` + `artifacts/plans/build-plan.md`.

